{
  "stem": "26111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The man was quite brilliant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He became a very close friend of my father's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He ended up psychoanalyzing him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so that, one way or another-- I don't know the details-- but through a combination of the analysis of specialized courses, of seminars with Jung, of doing papers with Jung, et cetera, et cetera-- and, and a very small, elite kind of groups of other people that were aspiring, aspiring psychoanalytic-- and, of course, others that were already in the field.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a quite young branch of psychoanalysis at that time, you must remember, not like the Freudian one, which was really ruling the roost at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, to cut a long story short, by '36, he was ready to open a-- sorry, to start himself in a psychoanalytic practice.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He couldn't do that in Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The only place where he could possibly do that in Germany would be Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so we moved to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he did exactly that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a dual purpose because the other purpose that certainly was a contributing factor was the treatment that we children-- my sister and I-- were getting in the school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- I wasn't able to hide my bloodiness-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents got a pretty good idea as to what was-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Franz Grunbaum, G-R-U-N-B-A-U-M.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, [SIGHS] there was-- not that you moved from pure black into pure white, no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was far, far, far better than Konigsberg for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One reason was that [SIGHS] the Olympic Games were slated to start within a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We moved there in April '36.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all, all the Nazis and everybody was on their very best behavior.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's an old story.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
